snippet.title: AMBER HEARD DEPOSITION PARODY
snippet.description:
This is a parody created for entertainment purposes only. 
Amber Heard claimed Johnny Depp abused her, but evidence has been showing otherwise.
Sharing some links down here, of the deposition and a few analysis videos of AH behavior during the deposition that I find super funny, hope you enjoy!

Stay tuned for more videos!  Thanks for watching!
